The website should have a secure login feature that ensures only authorized users can access the website's features. 
Upon entering the website, the user should be presented with a login page where they can sign in with their Google 
account. Before entering any information, the user should only be able to view the login page and no other information. 
Once the user has successfully logged in, they should be able to fully access the website's features, such as 
searching for recipes, viewing tutorials, and saving their favorite recipes.
